headline: Eli Lilly extends Purdue alliance; EMA investigates Valneva shot
summary: The big pharma will spend up to $250 million over the next eight years of the collaboration. Elsewhere, CRISPR Therapeutics unveiled new data and Vivo Capital raised funds.
